20challenge%20we%20have%20is%20we%20really%2C%20frankly%2C%20didn't%20put%20any%20guardrails%20around%20the%20program%20to%20help%20us%20scope%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltogether%2C%20these%20programs%20cost%20the%20Army%20roughly%20%24278%20million%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Credential%20Assistance%20program%20provides%20soldiers%20with%20%244%2C000%20dollars%20a%20year%20going%20toward%20earning%20various%20certifications%2C%20and%20the%20Tuition%20Assistance%20program%20allows%20active-duty%20service%20members%20to%20receive%20%24250%20per%20hour%20of%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWormuth%20emphasized%20that%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffederalnewsnetwork.com%2Farmy%2F2024%2F04%2Farmy-considering-cuts-to-education-programs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewants%20to%20keep%3C%2Fa%3E%20these%20programs%20but%20believes%20the%20number%20of%20credits%20and%20certifications%20soldiers%20can%20receive%20should%20be%20capped%20to%20manage%20costs.%20The%20qualifications%20making%20troops%20eligible%20for%20these%20programs%20could%20also%20be%20tightened%20as%20another%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20kinds%20of%20guardrails%20are%20very%20similar%20to%20what%20our%20sister%20services%20have%20done%20in%20the%20Air%20Force%20and%20the%20Navy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20obviously%20want%20to%20keep%20them.%20That's%20our%20number%20one%20goal%2C%20is%20to%20keep%20everybody.%20But%20how%20we%20transition%20them%20is%20critically%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Army%20is%20thoroughly%20reviewing%20the%20program%2C%20a%20service%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20explaining%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20must%20implement%20the%20programs%20in%20a%20way%20that%20not%20only%20maximizes%20the%20benefit%20for%20our%20Soldiers%2C%20but%20also%20puts%20rules%20in%20place%20that%20ensure%20the%20responsible%20stewardship%20of%20resources%20and%20continued%20program%20viabili