of%20the%20state's%2042%20seats.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP-dominated%20northeastern%20states%20saw%20high%20turnout%20--%20Assam%2072.3%20per%20cent%2C%20Meghalaya%2074.5%20per%20cent%2C%20Manipur%2069.2%20per%20cent%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2067.7%20per%20cent%20and%20tiny%20Tripura%20a%20whopping%2080.6%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20Bengal%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20workers%20clashed%20in%20Cooch%20Behar%20and%20accused%20each%20other%20of%20violence%2C%20intimidating%20voters%20and%20assault%20on%20poll%20agents%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%20The%20police%20denied%20any%20violence%20took%20place.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20a%20burst%20of%20gunfire%20was%20reported%20from%20a%20polling%20station%20in%20Bishnupur.%20In%20Imphal%20East%20district%2C%20a%20polling%20station%20was%20vandalised.%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20two%20elderly%20people%20--%20one%20a%2077-year-old%20woman%20--%20died%20at%20polling%20booths%20in%20Salem%20district.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20projecting%20huge%20confidence%20about%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20had%20won%20only%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20seats%20up%20for%20grabs%20today%20in%20the%20last%20general%20election.%20The%20NDA%20had%20won%2041%20of%20these%20seats%20and%20the%20UPA%2045.%20Six%20of%20the%20seats%20have%20been%20redrawn%20as%20part%20of%20delimitation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20its%20target%20of%20370%20seats%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20heavily%20banking%20on%20south%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20especially%20Tamil%20Nadu%20--%20where%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20open%20its%20account%20--%20and%20Bengal.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20today%2C%20Union%20minister%20and%20the%20BJP's%20chief%20strategist%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20PM%20Modi's%20popularity%20%26quot%3Bwill%20translate%20into%20our%20best%20showing%20in%20the%20south%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20pushed%20out%20of%20mu