20voting%20for%20NDA%20in%20record%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1781352849428877646%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolling%20took%20place%20in%20102%20constituencies%20across%2021%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20in%20the%20first%20of%20the%20seven-phase%20elections.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20described%20the%20turnout%20as%20%26quot%3Bhigh%26quot%3B%2C%20noting%20that%20voting%20remained%20%26quot%3Blargely%20peaceful%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20voter%20turnout%20was%20recorded%20at%2069.43%20per%20cent.%20Some%20constituencies%20were%20different%20then%20and%20the%20total%20number%20of%20seats%20which%20went%20to%20the%20polls%20were%2091.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20was%20reported%20from%20some%20areas%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20ethnic%20crisis-hit%20Manipur.%20Inner%20Manipur%20Congress%20candidate%20A%20Bimol%20Akoijam%20alleged%20BJP%20workers%20and%20an%20armed%20group%20stopped%20people%20from%20coming%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20to%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20four%20incidents%20of%20people%20breaking%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20in%20Inner%20Manipur%20polling%20booths%20were%20reported.%20The%20people%20got%20upset%20allegedly%20over%20proxy%20voting%20by%20an%20armed%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20Mizoram%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20Union%20Territories%20of%20Puducherry%2C%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20and%20Lakshadweep%20completed%20their%20voting%20process%20today%20in%20a%20single-phase%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20people%20in%2056%20villages%20in%20Bastar%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20cast%20their%20vote%20in%20polling%20booths