5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fpulse%2Fdo-you-have-enough-non-debt-money-ray-dalio-cfffe%2F%3FtrackingId%3DUEWd0393SuqIrVIjr5sjiQ%253D%253D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20post%20on%20LinkedIn%20this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistory%20and%20logic%20show%20that%20when%20there%20are%20big%20risks%20that%20the%20debts%20will%20either%201)%20not%20be%20paid%20back%20or%202)%20be%20paid%20back%20with%20money%20of%20depreciated%20value%2C%20the%20debt%20and%20the%20money%20become%20unattractive%2C%26quot%3B%20Dalio%20wrote%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20nations%20are%20deeply%20indebted%2C%20central%20banks%20are%20likely%20to%20print%20out%20more%20cash%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20debt%2C%20he%20noted%2C%20which%20is%20itself%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20prevents%20a%20big%20debt%20squeeze%20from%20happening%20by%20devaluing%20the%20money%20(i.e.%2C%20inflation)%2C%26quot%3B%20Dalio%20warned.%20%26quot%3BGold%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20a%20non-debt-backed%20form%20of%20money.%20It's%20like%20cash%2C%20except%20unlike%20cash%20and%20bonds%2C%20which%20are%20devalued%20by%20risks%20of%20default%20or%20inflation%2C%20gold%20is%20supported%20by%20risks%20of%20debt%20defaults%20and%20inflation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20main%20reason%20Dalio%20says%20he%20has%20gold%20in%20his%20own%20investment%20portfolio%2C%20he%20added%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20diversifier%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20high%20debt%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20has%20been%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fgold-price-all-time-record-safe-haven-rate-hike-geopolitics-2024-3%5C%22%3Ea%20record-setting%20run%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20Investors%20have%20been%20keen%20to%20buy%20the%20precious%20metal%20amid%20the%20looming%20risk%20of%20recession%20and%20inflation%20remaining%20stuck%20at%20elevated%20level