vitamin%20B7)%20is%20essential%20for%20the%20production%20of%20keratin%2C%20a%20protein%20that%20makes%20up%20the%20structure%20of%20hair%20and%20helps%20strengthen%20hair%20follicles%2C%20preventing%20breakage%20and%20promoting%20overall%20hair%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explains.%20%26quot%3BMeanwhile%2C%20caffeine%20helps%20stimulate%20blood%20circulation%20and%20deliver%20nutrients%20to%20hair%20while%20also%20counteracting%20the%20effects%20of%20dihydrotestosterone%20(DHT)%2C%20a%20hormone%20associated%20with%20hair%20loss.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20longtime%20fan%20of%20Brigeo's%20whole%20haircare%20line%20because%20the%20products%20are%20clean%2C%20emphasize%20naturally%20derived%20ingredients%2C%20and%20always%20contain%20nutrients%20with%20well-studied%20benefits.%20This%20shampoo%20is%20no%20exception%2C%20with%20scalp-stimulating%20and%20antioxidant-rich%20green%20coffee%20oil%2C%20copper%20peptides%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F17703734%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epromote%20hair%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20lindera%20strychnifolia%20root%20extract%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F32803888%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%2C%20balanced%20scalp%20microbiome%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20never%20get%20tired%20of%20the%20warm%20vanilla-tinged%2C%20fruit-forward%20scent%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20worth%20noting%20is%20that%20if%20you%20already%20have%20super%20dry%20hair%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20follow%20this%20up%20with%20an%20extra-rich%20conditioner%20or%20mask%2C%20as%20it%20can%20be%20a%20tad%20drying.%20That's%20pretty%20standard%20for%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-shampoos-for-thinning-hair%5C%22%3Eshampoo%20made%20for%20thin%20hair%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20%E2%80%94%20these%20formulas%20don't%20tend%20to%20contain%20some%20of%20the%20richer%20oils%20that%20may%20weigh%20thinner%20strands%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20curly%20hair%3Cp%3ECurly%20hair%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aad.org%2Fpublic%2Feveryday-care%2Fhair-scalp-care%2Fhair%2Fcurly-hair-care%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20prone%20to%20dryness%20and%20frizz%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20means%20you'll%20want%20to%20look%20for%20shampoos%20that%20are%20formulated%20with%20lots%20of%20moisturizing%20ingredients%20that%20can%20penetrate%20the%20hair%20shaft%2C%20leaving%20hair%20softer%2C%20smoother%2C%20and%20more%20elastic.%20Hence%2C%20it's%20less%20vulnerable%20to%20breakage.%20This%20one%20fits%20the%20bill%3A%20the%20formula%20includes%20nourishing%20cupua%C3%A7u%20seed%20butter%2C%20glycerin%2C%20and%20sunflower%20seed%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frthvi.com%2Fpages%2Ffounder%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeerika%20Khanna%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20certified%20trichologist%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frthvi.com%2Fpages%2Ffounder%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERthvi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20this%20shampoo%20is%20not%20only%20great%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-shampoos-for-curly-hair%5C%22%3Ecurly%20hair%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20features%20ingredients%20to%20support%20hair%20growth%20%E2%80%94%20like%20rosemary%20leaf%20extract.%20Some%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpubmed%2F25842469%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20found%20that%20rosemary%20extract%20is%20just%20as%20effective%20at%20protecting%20against%20hair%20loss%20as%20the%20medication%20minoxidil%20(commonly%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth%2Fminoxidil-beard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERogaine%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20and%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bmj.com%2Fbmj%2Fsection-pdf%2F186632%3Fpath%3D%2Fbmj%2F341%2F7766%2FClinical_Review.full.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20shown%20that%20it%20can%20stimulate%20hair%20growth%20in%20people%20with%20alopecia%20areata%20%E2%80%94%20an%20autoimmune%20disorder%20that%20causes%20hair%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20breakage%3Cp%3EBetween%20bleaching%20it%20every%20few%20months%20and%20heat%20styling%20it%20almost%20every%20time%20I%20shower%2C%20I%20put%20my%20poor%20hair%20through%20the%20wringer.%20I've%20been%20hard-pressed%20to%20find%20shampoos%20that%20don't%20leave%20my%20already%20dry%20hair%20feeling%20like%20straw%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%2C%20until%20I%20discovered%20Olaplex%20No.%204.%20The%20formula%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20a%20luxuriously%20creamy%20feel%20%E2%80%94%20is%20packed%20with%20plant-based%20oils%20and%20other%20ultra-moisturizing%20ingredients%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20overboard%20with%20conditioner%20afterward.%20But%20the%20real%20advantage%20to%20this%20shampoo%2C%20according%20to%20Han%2C%20lies%20in%20Olaplex's%20patented%20ingredient%3A%20bis-aminopropyl%20diglycol%20dimaleate.%20(Say%20that%20five%20times%20fast.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20helps%20to%20restore%20strength%20in%20the%20hair%20shaft%20by%20repairing%20broken%20bonds%20that%20occur%20because%20of%20exposure%20to%20chemicals%2Fdyes%2C%20heat%2C%20and%20UV%20rays.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20that%2C%20but%20this%20shampoo%20features%20moisture-boosting%20hyaluronic%20acid%2C%20strengthening%20plant-based%20protein%2C%20and%20rosemary%20leaf%20extract%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS2468227622001302%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20hair%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20subtle%20yet%20refreshing%20grapefruit-tinged%20scent%20doesn't%20hurt%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheck%20out%20some%20of%20our%20other%20favorite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Folaplex-dupes%5C%22%3Ebond-building%20treatments%3C%2Fa%3E%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20thickening%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20exactly%20what%20happened%20between%20my%2020s%20and%2030s%2C%20but%20my%20previously%20thick%20tresses%20have%20been%20getting%20gradually%20thinner.%20It's%20a%20bummer%20because%20even%20though%20I%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20hair%2C%20it%20doesn't%20look%20like%20much%20%E2%80%94%20leaving%20me%20with%20pretty%20sad-looking%20ponytails%20and%20buns.%20That's%20why%20I've%20prioritized%20thickening%20shampoos%20like%20this%20derm-approved%20one%2C%20which%20has%20a%20pretty%20impressive%20ingredient%20list.%20I%20also%20happen%20to%20like%20the%20clean%2C%20faintly%20floral%20scent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20shampoo%20contains%20amaranth%20extract%20which%20acts%20as%20a%20natural%20hair%20strengthener%20and%20also%20has%20ceramides%20and%20biotin%20to%20improve%20the%20strength%20of%20each%20strand%2C%20preventing%20premature%20breakage%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Han.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBondiBoost's%20longtime%20star%20ingredient%20is%20Australian%20aloe%20vera%20powder%2C%20which%20may%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F342588964_A_Close_Look_at_Aloe_Vera_Barbadensis_and_It%2527s_Effect_on_Hair_Health%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20restore%20lost%20moisture%20in%20the%20hair%20and%20fortify%20the%20hair%20cuticles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20shampoo%20also%20contains%20vegan%20marine%20collagen%2C%20which%20contains%20some%20nonessential%20amino%20acids%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0079642515000596%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebody%20uses%20to%20build%20keratin%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4201279%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emain%20building%20block%20of%20healthy%20hair%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20strengthening%3Cp%3EI'll%20admit%20I%20was%20skeptical%20when%20I%20read%20the%20instructions%20on%20this%20concentrated%20shampoo%2C%20which%20advised%20using%20half%20the%20amount%20I%20usually%20do.%20Alas%2C%20I%20got%20a%20pretty%20rich%20lather%20despite%20applying%20much%20less%20product.%20That%20means%20the%20bottle%20lasts%20way%20longer%20despite%20taking%20up%20less%20space%20in%20my%20shower.%20I%20love%20the%20uplifting%2C%20lemony%20scent%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20leaves%20my%20hair%20feeling%20soft%2C%20bouncy%2C%20and%20more%20manageable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Levine%2C%20the%20best%20shampoos%20for%20hair%20growth%20contain%20collagen%20and%2For%20keratin.%20This%20product%20has%20both.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCollagen%20provides%20essential%20amino%20acids%20that%20support%20the%20structure%20of%20hair%20follicles%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Keratin%2C%20a%20protein%20that%20makes%20up%20the%20structure%20of%20hair%20and%20helps%20strengthen%20hair%20follicles%2C%20prevents%20breakage%2C%20and%20promotes%20overall%20hair%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHan%20also%20recommends%20looking%20for%20shampoos%20that%20are%20packed%20with%20peptides%2C%20which%20this%20product%20also%20has%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20addition%20of%20hydrolyzed%20yeast%20protein.%20Peptides%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8332470%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20scalp%20and%20hair%20hydration%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well%20as%20hair%20follicle%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20hair%20loss%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20have%20noticed%20cannabidiol%20(CBD)%20popping%20up%20in%20more%20haircare%20and%20other%20products%20as%20of%20late%2C%20and%20that's%20no%20surprise%20when%20you%20consider%20that%20it%20can%20help%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4151231%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregulate%20sebum%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20improved%20scalp%20health.%20In%20fact%2C%20participants%20in%20a%20small%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10212262%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2021%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20applied%20CBD%20topically%20every%20day%20for%20six%20months%2C%20and%20researchers%20observed%20a%2093.5%25%20increase%20in%20hair%20count%20%E2%80%94%20with%20no%20side%20effects%2C%20to%20boot.%20CBD%20is%20the%20superstar%20ingredient%20in%20this%20innovative%20shampoo%2C%20which%20also%20leverages%20the%20silk%20protein%20and%20vegan%20keratin%20alternative%20Karmatin%E2%84%A2.%20All%20of%20that%20may%20help%20to%20explain%20why%20in%20a%20study%20of%20150%20users%2C%2091%25%20saw%20an%20improvement%20in%20the%20appearance%20of%20their%20hair%20after%20using%20this%20shampoo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoakye%20says%20aloe%20vera%20juice%20is%20one%20of%20her%20favorite%20ingredients%20to%20look%20for%20in%20shampoos%20for%20hair%20growth%2C%20and%20this%20formula%20happens%20to%20feature%20it.%20Studies%20show%20that%20aloe%20has%20scalp-calming%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC2763764%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanti-inflammatory%20properties%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsaudijournals.com%2Fmedia%2Farticles%2FSIJAP_51_1-8.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboost%20blood%20circulation%20to%20the%20scalp%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F233818204_Medicinal_and_cosmetological_importance_of_Aloe_vera%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearchers%3C%2Fa%3E%20believe%20aloe%20vera%20may%20also%20help%20with%20hair%20growth%20because%20it%20can%20increase%20the%20delivery%20of%20nutrients%20and%20oxygen%20to%20the%20hair%20follicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20standout%20ingredient%3F%20Arginine%20%E2%80%94%20an%20important%20amino%20acid%20found%20in%20the%20hair%20that%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F33878855%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20help%20shedding%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thus%20helping%20you%20achieve%20a%20fuller%20mane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20luxury%3Cp%3EThis%20gentle%20yet%20nourishing%20shampoo%20has%20definitely%20achieved%20cult-favorite%20status%2C%20and%20it's%20easy%20to%20see%20why.%20Oribe%20Gold%20Lust%20is%20packed%20with%20healing%20and%20moisturizing%20oils%20and%20butters%20%E2%80%94%20like%20argan%20oil%2C%20shea%20butter%2C%20and%20maracuja%20%E2%80%94%20and%20other%20powerful%20ingredients%20like%20biotin%2C%20plant%20collagen%2C%20and%20plant-based%20protein.%20It%20also%20has%20scalp-invigorating%20caffeine%2C%20which%20Khanna%20and%20Levine%20say%20is%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20hair%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCaffeine%20helps%20stimulate%20blood%20circulation%20and%20deliver%20nutrients%20to%20hair%20while%20also%20counteracting%20the%20effects%20of%20dihydrotestosterone%20(DHT)%2C%20a%20hormone%20associated%20with%20hair%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Levine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredients%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20shampoos%20for%20hair%20growth%20will%20contain%20the%20following%2C%20according%20to%20dermatologists%20and%20trichologists%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKeratin%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBiotin%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmino%20acids%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPeptides%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHyaluronic%20acid%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EArgan%20or%20jojoba%20oil%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERosemary%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESaw%20palmetto%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20natural%20ingredients%20have%20been%20shown%20to%20promote%20increased%20strength%20and%20integrity%20of%20existing%20hairs%20while%20decreasing%20the%20potential%20for%20shedding%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Han.%20Rosemary%20and%20saw%20palmetto%20also%20demonstrate%20the%20ability%20to%20inhibit%20or%20block%20dihydrotestosterone%20(DHT)%2C%20a%20hormone%20that%20can%20be%20toxic%20to%20hair%20follicles.%20The%20others%20are%20geared%20more%20toward%20improving%20the%20strength%20of%20hair%20and%20repairing%20damage%20to%20the%20hair%20shaft%20that%20can%20occur%20with%20heat%2C%20styling%2C%20and%20environmental%20exposures%20such%20as%20UV%20radiation%20and%20pollution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20what%20to%20avoid%2C%20Levine%2C%20Boakye%2C%20and%20Khanna%20advise%20skipping%20shampoos%20that%20contain%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EParabens%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESulfates%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESynthetic%20fragrances%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHair%20type%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aad.org%2Fpublic%2Feveryday-care%2Fhair-scalp-care%2Fhair%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Academy%20of%20Dermatology%3C%2Fa%3E%20(AAD)%20strongly%20advises%20opting%20for%20a%20shampoo%20that's%20formulated%20specifically%20for%20your%20hair%20type%20to%20ensure%20it's%20tailored%20to%20your%20needs.%20Otherwise%2C%20you%20likely%20won't%20reap%20the%20benefits%20you're%20looking%20for%20%E2%80%94%20or%20worse%2C%20you%20could%20risk%20damaging%20your%20hair%2C%20says%20Levine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20coal%20tar%20(a%20common%20ingredient%20in%20anti-dandruff%20shampoos%20and%20conditioners)%20isn't%20suitable%20for%20light-colored%20hair%20due%20to%20the%20risk%20of%20discoloration%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Han.%20%26quot%3BFor%20people%20with%20fine%20hair%2C%20I%20generally%20suggest%20products%20without%20heavy%20ingredients%20that%20might%20make%20the%20hair%20look%20more%20flat%20and%20limp.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20shea%20butter%2C%20coconut%20oil%2C%20and%20sunflower%20oil%20are%20all%20super%20hydrating%20and%20perfectly%20suited%20to%20medium%20to%20thick%20dry%20hair%20but%20will%20probably%20weigh%20down%20fine%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinoxidil%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevine%20says%20the%20medication%20minoxidil%20(commonly%20known%20by%20the%20brand%20name%20Rogaine)%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6691938%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20beneficial%20for%20some%20people%20with%20severe%20hair%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20androgenetic%20alopecia%20and%20other%20hair%20disorders.%20However%2C%20Han%20notes%20that%20it's%20not%20safe%20for%20anyone%20who%20is%20pregnant%20or%20breastfeeding%20and%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F34370845%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoison%20dogs%20and%20cats%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20small%20amounts.%20Minoxidil%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK482378%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20suitable%20for%20anyone%20under%20the%20age%20of%2018%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20anyone%20who%20has%20experienced%20scalp%20infections%20or%20inflammation%2C%20hair%20loss%20after%20childbirth%2C%20or%20sudden%2Fpatchy%20hair%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHan%20notes%20that%20oral%20minoxidil%20tends%20to%20have%20more%20severe%20side%20effects%20than%20the%20topical%20version%20of%20this%20production.%20That%20said%2C%20topical%20minoxidil%20can%20still%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK482378%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecause%20unpleasant%20or%20concerning%20side%20effects%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESkin%20irritation%20that%20can%20worsen%20eczema%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EItching%20and%2For%20a%20burning%20sensation%20on%20the%20scalp%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESkin%20scaling%2C%20which%20can%20worsen%20the%20scalp%20condition%20seborrheic%20dermatitis%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExcessive%20hair%20shedding%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExcessive%20body%20hair%20growth%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20Han%20and%20Levine%20advise%20consulting%20with%20a%20board-certified%20dermatologist.%20They%20will%20consider%20your%20scalp%20health%2C%20overall%20health%20history%2C%20and%20other%20factors%20before%20determining%20whether%20Minoxidil%20is%20right%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRosemary%20oil%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20offer%20similar%20benefits%20to%20minoxidil%20in%20clinical%20studies%2C%20making%20it%20a%20viable%20alternative%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Khanna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F25842469%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2015%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20participants%20with%20androgenetic%20alopecia%20used%20either%20topical%20minoxidil%20or%20rosemary%20oil%20on%20their%20scalp.%20When%20researchers%20examined%20their%20hair%20at%20a%20three-month%20and%20six-month%20follow-up%2C%20both%20groups%20experienced%20equal%20growth.%20However%2C%20the%20minoxidil%20participants%20experienced%20more%20scalp%20itching%20than%20those%20who%20used%20rosemary%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch3%3EWhat%20causes%20hair%20loss%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Levine%2C%20hair%20loss%20can%20be%20caused%20by%20a%20number%20of%20factors%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHormonal%20imbalances%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20polycystic%20ovary%20syndrome%20(PCOS)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGenetics%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUnderlying%20medical%20conditions%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESide%20effects%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americanhairloss.org%2Fdrug_induced_hair_loss%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecertain%20medications%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20like%20blood%20thinners%2C%20antifungals%2C%20beta-blockers%2C%20antidepressants%2C%20anticonvulsants%2C%20and%20acne%20treatments%20with%20vitamin%20A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStress%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENutritional%20deficiencies%2C%20like%20low%20iron%20levels%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGenetics%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20pattern%20hair%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Han.%20%26quot%3BGenetically-driven%20hair%20loss%20is%20progressive%20and%20will%20worsen%20over%20time%20without%20treatment.%20Reversing%20and%2For%20treating%20the%20underlying%20medical%20issue%20is%20important%20in%20optimizing%20the%20chances%20of%20hair%20regrowth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHan%20also%20notes%20that%20hormonal%20changes%20are%20another%20common%20cause%20of%20hair%20loss%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20in%20those%20assigned%20female%20at%20birth.%20This%20can%20happen%20as%20a%20result%20of%20pregnancy%2C%20childbirth%2C%20and%20menopause.%20In%20people%20assigned%20male%20at%20birth%2C%20Khanna%20says%20this%20is%20usually%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmy.clevelandclinic.org%2Fhealth%2Farticles%2F24555-dht-dihydrotestosterone%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIncreased%2520DHT%2520activity%2520at%2520your%2Ccycle%252C%2520resulting%2520in%2520hair%2520loss.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelated%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20dihydrotestosterone%20(DHT)%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20hair%20follicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20underlying%20hormonal%20shifts%20that%20occur%20during%20these%20events%20are%20thought%20to%20play%20a%20role%20and%20can%20unmask%20the%20underlying%20genetic%20predisposition%20of%20progressive%20hair%20loss%20in%20some%20individuals%2C%26quot%3B%20Han%20explains.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20all%20people%20assigned%20male%20at%20birth%20will%20have%20detectable%20levels%20of%20DHT%20%E2%80%94%20why%20some%20progress%20to%20baldness%20and%20others%20don't%20may%20be%20related%20to%20how%20sensitive%20their%20hair%20follicles%20are%20to%20DHT%20which%20is%20ultimately%20driven%20by%20genetics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20you%20treat%20your%20hair%20loss%20will%20depend%20on%20what's%20triggering%20it.%20That's%20why%20Boakye%20advises%20seeing%20a%20dermatologist%20or%20trichologist%20who%20can%20help%20you%20identify%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20your%20hair%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDoes%20shampoo%20help%20hair%20growth%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShampoo%20works%20to%20clean%20the%20scalp%20and%20hair%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20can%20promote%20hair%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Boakye.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20results%20will%20vary%20depending%20on%20individual%20hair%20type%20and%20based%20on%20consistent%20use.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHair%20growth%20shampoos%20can%20help%20if%20poor%20scalp%20health%20is%20to%20blame%20for%20hair%20thinning%20or%20shedding.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20Boakye%2C%20even%20the%20best%20shampoos%20for%20hair%20growth%20are%20less%20likely%20to%20yield%20results%20if%20there%20are%20underlying%20reasons%20for%20your%20hair%20loss%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20genetics%2C%20nutritional%20deficiencies%2C%20and%20hormone%20imbalances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShampoos%20formulated%20for%20hair%20loss%20or%20thinning%20can%20help%20slow%20down%20these%20conditions%2C%20but%20they%20won't%20reverse%20them%20or%20actually%20cause%20hair%20to%20regrow%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Han.%20I%20view%20them%20as%20complementary%20products%20that%20patients%20can%20add%20to%20their%20hair%20loss%20regimen%2C%20which%20usually%20features%20a%20prescription%20medication.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20regular%20shampoo%20and%20shampoo%20for%20hair%20growth%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRegular%20shampoos%20are%20formulated%20to%20clean%20and%20rid%20the%20hair%20of%20dirt%2C%20sweat%2C%20and%20unwanted%20oils%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Boakye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20distinguishes%20shampoo%20for%20hair%20growth%20is%20the%20inclusion%20of%20certain%20ingredients%20that%20are%20known%20to%20promote%20scalp%20and%20hair%20health%2C%20says%20Levine.%20These%20ingredients%20are%20intended%20to%20prevent%20breakage%20%E2%80%94%20thereby%20allowing%20the%20hair%20to%20grow%20longer%20%E2%80%94%20while%20also%20nourishing%20the%20scalp%20and%20hair%20follicles%20to%20support%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShampoos%20formulated%20for%20hair%20loss%20should%20contain%20ingredients%20with%20anti-inflammatory%20and%20antioxidizing%20properties%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Han.%20%26quot%3BMany%20shampoos%20formulated%20for%20hair%20loss%20may%20also%20contain%20ingredients%20that%20help%20optimize%20the%20scalp%20health%2C%20which%20is%20an%20important%20foundation%20for%20healthy%20follicles.%20If%20there%20are%20signs%20of%20inflammation%2C%20such%20as%20flaking%20and%20itching%2C%20it%20can%20be%20helpful%20to%20use%20these%20shampoos%20to%20promote%20a%20healthy%20scalp%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20long%20does%20it%20take%20to%20see%20results%20from%20shampoos%20for%20hair%20growth%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20expect%20to%20see%20results%20from%20your%20hair%20growth%20shampoo%20immediately%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20healthy%20hair%20only%20grows%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK513312%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHealthy%2520hair%2520growth%2520occurs%2520at%2Canagen%252C%2520catagen%2520and%2520telogen%2520phases.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E0.5%20inches%20per%20month%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Levine%20and%20Khanna%2C%20it%20typically%20takes%20at%20least%20three%20or%20four%20months%20to%20see%20any%20effects%20on%20your%20hair%20thickness%20or%20length.%20However%2C%20Khanna%20says%20you%20may%20notice%20improvements%20in%20your%20hair%20quality%20%E2%80%94%20the%20shine%2C%20softness%2C%20and%20strength%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%94%20after%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20of%20using%20these%20shampoos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-shampoos-hair-growth%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713540916000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662189bd49058e6693577ecb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-shampoos-hair-growth%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whether%20you're%20struggling%20with%20hair%20loss%20or%20crave%20more%20volume%2C%20the%20best%20shampoos%20for%20hair%20growth%20help%20improve%20scalp%20health%20which%20leads%20to%20thicker%2C%20fuller%20hair.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Strong)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-shampoos-hair-growth%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PFL%203%20Livestream%3A%20How%20to%20Watch%20Tonight%E2%80%99s%20Mixed%20Martial%20Arts%20Event%20Online%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713540893000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FGettyImages-2147761701.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235975724%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20of%20the%20best%20MMA%20fighters%20in%20the%20world%20are%20in%20Chicago%2C%20Illinois%20this%20weekend%20for%20PFL%203%20(Professional%20Fighters%20League).%20For%20the%20third%20event%20of%20the%202024%20regular%20sea