part%20from%20developing%20fronts%20from%20scratch%2C%20ITF%20also%20acquires%20fonts.%20Recently%2C%20it%20has%20acquired%20several%20independent%20foundries.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20launching%20a%20new%20umbrella-type%20foundry%20that%20will%20unite%20all%20our%20brands.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20expand%20our%20retail%20library.%20A%20key%20focus%20for%20us%20is%20ensuring%20our%20library%20is%20inclusive%2C%20representing%20not%20just%20English%20or%20Indian%20languages%20but%20also%20those%20that%20are%20endangered%20and%20less%20represented%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20inspirations%20in%20the%20sphere%20of%20typography%2C%20Satya%20names%20Adrian%20Frutiger%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Swiss%20type%20designer%20known%20for%20his%20clarity%20and%20functionality%20in%20fonts%20like%20Univers%20and%20Frutiger%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Herb%20Lubalin%20%E2%80%94%20a%20creative%20typographer%20who%20infused%20letters%20with%20emotion%20and%20narrative.%20Eric%20Gill%E2%80%99s%20harmonious%20blend%20of%20classic%20and%20modern%20styles%2C%20evident%20in%20typefaces%20like%20Gill%20Sans%20and%20Perpetua%2C%20has%20also%20guided%20his%20approach%20to%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20pioneers%20have%20shaped%20his%20understanding%20of%20how%20type%20can%20communicate%20beyond%20words%2C%20blending%20artistry%20with%20utility%2C%20says%20Satya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20823px)%20100vw%2C%20823px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FSatya-Rajpurohit-1713535695.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22823%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Satya%20co-founded%20Indian%20Type%20Foundry%20(ITF)%20in%202009%20in%20Ahmedabad.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FSatya-Rajpurohit-1713535695.jpeg%20823w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FSatya-R