3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109438644.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERanveer%20Singh%20denies%20endorsing%20any%20political%20party%20and%20says%20that%20the%20video%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20is%20AI%20generated%20'deepfake%20video'.%20The%20actor%20urges%20fans%20to%20beware%20of%20'deepfake'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Franveer-singh-reacts-to-his-deepfake-video-endorsing-a-political-party-deepfake-se-baccho%2Farticleshow%2F109438644.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Antarctica's%20France-Sized%20Ice%20Shelf%20Makes%20Jumps%2C%20Raising%20Icequake%20Concerns%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResearchers%20have%20uncovered%20a%20surprising%20phenomenon%20in%20Antarctica%3A%20the%20massive%20Ross%20Ice%20Shelf%2C%20roughly%20the%20size%20of%20France%2C%20lurches%20forward%20several%20centimetres%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20day.%20This%20movement%20is%20triggered%20by%20the%20Whillans%20Ice%20Stream%2C%20a%20fast-flowing%20river%20of%20ice%20that%20occasionally%20gets%20stuck%20and%20then%20surges%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20highlights%20a%20previously%20unknown%20aspect%20of%20ice%20shelf%20dynamics%20and%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20long-term%20stability%20of%20the%20Ross%20Ice%20Shelf%20in%20the%20face%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20has%20been%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fagupubs.onlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1029%2F2023GL108040%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGeophysical%20Research%20Letters.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESudden%20Shifts%2C%20Not%20Gradual%20Flow%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20most%20glaciers%20that%20creep%20at%20a%20glacial%20pace%2C%20the%20Whillans%20Ice%20Stream%20exhibits%20a%20stop-and-go%20motion.%20A%20lack%20of%20water%20lubrication%20beneath%20the%20stream%20may%20be%20causing%20it%20to%20intermittently%20stick%2C%20then%20release%20built-up%20pressure%20in%20sudden%20bursts.These%20jolts%2C%20similar%20to%20tremors%20along%20earthquake%20faults%2C%20push%20against%20the%20Ross%20Ice%20Shelf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIcequakes%20and%20Fractures%3A%20A%20Potential%20Threat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20daily%20jumps%20aren't%20directly%20linked%20to%20human-caused%20warming%2C%20they%20could%20contribute%20to%20the%20weakening%20of%20the%20Ross%20Ice%20Shelf.Ice%20shelves%20act%20as%20barriers%2C%20slowing%20the%20flow%20of%20glaciers%20and%20ice%20streams%20into%20the%20ocean.If%20the%20Ross%20Ice%20Shelf%20weakens%20and%20breaks%20apart%2C%20it%20could%20accelerate%20ice%20melt%20rates%20and%20sea%20level%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScientists%20are%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20closely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20team%20emphasises%20that%20icequakes%20and%20fractures%20are%20natural%20occurrences%20on%20ice%20shelves.%20However%2C%20they%20will%20be%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20Ross%20Ice%20Shelf%20for%20signs%20of%20disintegration%2C%20similar%20to%20what%20has%20happened%20to%20smaller%20ice%20shelves%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20study%20highlights%20the%20complex%20and%20dynamic%20nature%20of%20Antarctic%20ice%20shelves%20and%20the%20need%20for%20continued%20research%20to%20understand%20their%20future%20under%20a%20changing%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713533040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F2ct08hc_ross-ice-shelf_625x300_19_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fross-ice-shelf-antarcticas-france-sized-ice-shelf-makes-daily-jumps-raising-icequake-concerns-5478464%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20potential%20acceleration%20and%20eventual%20disintegration%20of%20the%20Ross%20Ice%20Shelf%2C%20leading%20to%20its%20movement%20into%20the%20sea%2C%20would%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences%20for%20ice%20coverage%20throughout%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fross-ice-shelf-antarcticas-france-sized-ice-shelf-makes-daily-jumps-raising-icequake-concerns-5478464%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fross-ice-shelf-antarcticas-france-sized-ice-shelf-makes-daily-jumps-raising-icequake-concerns-5478464%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fross-ice-shelf-antarcticas-france-sized-ice-shelf-makes-daily-jumps-raising-icequake-concerns-5478464%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22InterGlobe%2C%20Archer%20Aviation%20plan%20electric%20air%20taxis%20from%20CP%20to%20Gurugram%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713532700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F09%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1699534440-2698.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finterglobe-archer-aviation-plan-electric-air-taxis-from-cp-to-gurugram-124041901009_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Archer%20Aviation%20will%20supply%20200%20electric%20vertical%20takeoff%20and%20landing%20(eVTOL)%20aircraft%20that%20can%20carry%20four%20passengers%20besides%20a%20pilot%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finterglobe-archer-aviation-plan-electric-air-taxis-from-cp-to-gurugram-124041901009_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Finterglobe-archer-aviation-plan-electric-air-taxis-from-cp-to-gurugram-124041901009_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.b