0to%20over%2020%20women%20in%20Mainpuri%2C%20as%20the%20process%20of%20growing%20saffron%20is%20laborious.%20Right%20from%20drying%20the%20bulbs%20to%20plucking%20each%20stigma%2C%20drying%2C%20and%20packing%20them%2C%20it%20requires%20careful%20and%20precise%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20like%20Geeta%20Devi%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20dependable%20income.%20At%2040%20years%20old%2C%20she%E2%80%99s%20a%20mother%20of%20five%20and%20the%20primary%20provider%20for%20her%20family.%20Previously%2C%20she%20laboured%20in%20the%20fields%20under%20the%20scorching%20sun%2C%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20Work%20was%20inconsistent%2C%20and%20income%20was%20meagre%2C%20she%20recalls.%20However%2C%20since%20joining%20Shubhavni%20Farms%20last%20July%2C%20her%20situation%20has%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20enjoy%20the%20work%20here%20and%20brought%20in%2020%20more%20women.%20We%20were%20taught%20everything%20about%20saffron%20cultivation%20and%20did%20everything%20from%20aeration%20to%20keeping%20it%20clean%20and%20removing%20the%20stamen%20from%20the%20flower.%20We%20are%20working%20in%20a%20comfortable%20environment%20instead%20of%20bearing%20the%20harsh%20heat.%20We%20get%20paid%20at%20least%20Rs%20100%20more%20per%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Geeta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20Shubha%E2%80%99s%20dream%20to%20provide%20a%20regular%20source%20of%20income%20to%20more%20women%20like%20Geeta%20and%20ensure%20that%20their%20children%20have%20a%20better%20future.%20And%20to%20every%20woman%20wanting%20to%20start%20a%20business%2C%20she%20has%20one%20message%2C%20%E2%80%9CNever%20underestimate%20yourself%20and%20your%20dreams.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20believe%20that%20we%20are%20no%20longer%20a%20patriarchal%20society.%20We%20are%20equally%20capable.%20Self-reliance%20gives%20immense%20confidence%20and%20gives%20you%20an%20opportunity%20to%20inspire%20others.%20Even%20starting%20a%20small%20business%20will%20boost%20