p%3EShe%20wanted%20to%20study%20psychology%20to%20%E2%80%9Cknow%20the%20answers%E2%80%9D%20about%20why%20people%20behave%20a%20certain%20way%20and%20who%20deserves%20what.%20She%20managed%20to%20secure%20admission%20to%20a%20Government%20school%20for%20Class%2011.%20Little%20did%20Sandhya%20know%20that%20her%20life%20would%20soon%20change%20forever%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20newspaper%20cutting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20revolution%20in%20a%20red%20light%20district%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20in%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20California-based%20Robin%20Chaurasiya%20started%20volunteering%20with%20NGOs%20across%20the%20world.%20In%202008%2C%20she%20worked%20with%20an%20NGO%20that%20rescued%20and%20rehabilitated%20girls%20from%20brothels.%20The%20problem%2C%20she%20found%2C%20was%20that%20after%20six%20months%20to%20a%20year%2C%20the%20girls%20ended%20up%20going%20back%20to%20the%20brothels%2C%20or%20were%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20300px)%20100vw%2C%20300px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-14-min-1713343005-300x300.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girls%20at%20Kranti%20get%20an%20opportunity%20to%20achieve%20their%20potential%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-14-min-1713343005-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-14-min-1713343005-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-14-min-1713343005-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-08-at-19.44.56-14-min-1713343005-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2