ortunities%2C%20and%20resources%20as%20people%20from%20privileged%20backgrounds%2C%20they%20will%20become%20revolutionary%20leaders%20%E2%80%94%20more%20innovative%2C%20compassionate%2C%20and%20resilient%20due%20to%20their%20life%20experiences.%20We%20want%20to%20harness%20their%20power%20as%20agents%20of%20social%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Robin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%20provides%20shelter%2C%20education%2C%20support%20and%20opportunities%20for%20girls%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2012%20and%2021.%20Kranti%20has%20its%20own%20school%20with%20six%20teachers%20and%20a%20curriculum%20that%20includes%20English%2C%20reading%2C%20writing%2C%20geography%2C%20music%2C%20creative%20thinking%2C%20yoga%2C%20and%20meditation%2C%20along%20with%20regular%20school%20subjects%2C%20health%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%20also%20has%20a%20social%20justice%20curriculum%20which%20covers%2020%20topics%20such%20as%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20religion%2C%20environment%2C%20gender%2Fsexuality%2C%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights.%20The%20girls%20are%20taught%20about%20the%20problems%20and%20what%20they%20can%20do%20to%20solve%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20equips%20students%20to%20join%20mainstream%20schools%2C%20if%20they%20wish%20to%2C%20or%20help%20others%20through%20open%20schooling.%20While%20many%20girls%20have%20gone%20abroad%20to%20study%2C%20for%20some%2C%20just%20managing%20to%20stay%20afloat%20is%20a%20big%20win%2C%20according%20to%20Robin%2C%20which%20is%20why%20therapy%20is%20given%20so%20much%20importance%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20810px)%20100vw%2C%20810px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FC0045T01-1713280710.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kranti%20runs%20it's%20own%20school%20for%20the%20girls%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FC0045T