ghter%20Overcame%20Crushing%20Poverty%20to%20Become%20a%20Celebrated%20MMA%20Champion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%209%20March%2C%202024%2C%20Chungreng%20Koren%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mixed%20martial%20arts%20(MMA)%20fighter%20from%20Manipur%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98The%20Indian%20Rhino%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20took%20his%20first%20step%20into%20the%20limelight%20at%20the%20Noida%20Indoor%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompeting%20in%20the%20co-main%20event%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290511%2Fanshul-jubli-road-to-ufc-best-indian-mma-fighter-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatrix%20Fight%20Night%3C%2Fa%3E%20(MFN-14)%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20MMA%20promotion%2C%20Chungreng%20Koren%20took%20on%20veteran%20fighter%20Mohammed%20Farhad%20in%20a%20five-round%20fight%20for%20the%20(Interim)%20Bantamweight%20Title%20(61%20kg).%20As%20the%20fighters%20made%20their%20respective%20walk-ins%20to%20the%20octagon%2C%20the%2016%2C000-strong%20crowd%20at%20the%20Noida%20Indoor%20Stadium%20cheered%20in%20anticipation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20was%20a%20dominant%20performance%20by%20Chungreng%20who%20took%20the%20veteran%20fighter%20down%20at%20will%20with%20his%20relentless%20wrestling%20and%20then%20struck%20him%20with%20a%20barrage%20of%20ground-and-pound%20strikes%20till%20the%20referee%20intervened%20at%20the%20end%20of%20Round%204.%20Following%20the%20fight%2C%20with%20the%20belt%20wrapped%20around%20his%20shoulder%2C%20he%20made%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20restore%20peace%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20facing%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20heartfelt%20appeal%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20moment%20also%20marked%20Chungreng%E2%80%99s%20emergence%20as%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20standout%20MMA%20fighters.%20When%20asked%20about%20the%20moment%20when%20he%20won%20the%20title%2C%20Chungreng%2