F326708%2Fdattu-agarwal-free-residential-school-for-girls-with-visual-impairment%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20people%20with%20visual%20impairment%20a%3C%2Fa%3End%20other%20disabilities%20%E2%80%94%20granting%20them%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2043%20years%2C%20through%20his%20organisation%2C%20he%20has%20been%20providing%20them%20with%20training%20in%20acupressure%2C%20loom%20operation%2C%20and%20graphic%20designing%20in%20digital%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20journey%20to%20independence%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarishchandra%20is%20the%20first%20university%20graduate%2C%20not%20only%20in%20his%20family%20but%20also%20in%20his%20entire%20village.%20Despite%20being%20a%20young%20man%20with%20extraordinary%20dreams%2C%20societal%20expectations%20nudged%20him%20towards%20seeking%20employment%20in%20the%20bustling%20%E2%80%9Cbig%20cities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20those%20pivotal%20moments%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%E2%80%99re%20the%20first%20in%20your%20family%20or%20village%20to%20successfully%20graduate%20from%20university%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20you.%20My%20father%20and%20the%20villagers%20anticipated%20that%20I%20would%20secure%20a%20job%20and%20contribute%20financially%20to%20the%20household.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Harishchandra%E2%80%99s%20aspirations%20diverged%20from%20conventional%20expectations.%20He%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20certain%20segments%20of%20society%20receive%20little%20to%20no%20assistance.%20They%20are%20often%20marginalised%20and%20forced%20to%20depend%20on%20others.%20Securing%20a%20job%20was%20never%20my%20intention%3B%20my%20goal%20was%20to%20assist%20the%20overlooked%20sections%20of%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20fondly%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Angel%20for%20the%20disabled%E2%80%99%2C%20Harishchandra%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20was%20a%20far%20cry