the%20organisation%2C%20Harishchandra%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20first%20person%20to%20graduate%20from%20college.%20I%20could%20have%20just%20stuck%20to%20a%20job%20and%20%E2%80%98given%20back%E2%80%99%20to%20my%20family%2C%20but%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20my%20education%20to%20give%20back%20to%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFoundation%20of%20the%20NGO%20%26amp%3B%20how%20you%20can%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarishchandra%20has%20spent%20decades%20of%20his%20life%20caring%20for%20the%20underserved.%20His%20son%20Prashant%20Sude%20is%20following%20in%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20footsteps%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20still%20works%20and%20stays%20every%20day%2C%20but%20I%20have%20now%20taken%20over%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20organisation.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20levels%20of%20interventions%20that%20we%20do%20to%20help%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20works%20to%20help%20people%20with%20disabilities%20by%20giving%20them%20training%20in%20different%20areas%20to%20help%20them%20become%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20our%20Swadhar%20Scheme%2C%20what%20we%20initially%20did%20was%20train%20them%20in%20recycling%20old%20%3Cem%3Esarees%20%3C%2Fem%3Einto%20mats.%20The%20disposal%20of%20old%20%3Cem%3Esarees%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20significant%20issue%2C%20contributing%20to%20environmental%20harm.%20At%20our%20hand-me-down%20centre%2C%20we%20recycle%20these%20sarees%20into%20mats%2C%20providing%20a%20sustainable%20solution%20to%20this%20problem.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20not%20only%20earn%20a%20livelihood%20but%20also%20contribute%20to%20addressing%20the%20environmental%20challenges%20associated%20with%20non-biodegradable%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20changing%20times%2C%20Prashant%20realised%20that%20this%20training%20might%20not%20be%20viable%20after%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20keep%20changing%20with%20time.%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20might%20not%20be%20a%20very%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294290%2Fcouple-shares-personal-finance-tips-for-relationships-smart-money-management-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancially%20smart%20occupation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20future.%20In%202010%2C%20we%20started%20giving%20acupressure%20and%20massage%20training%20to%20visually%20impaired%20people.%20Massage%20is%20an%20excellent%20livelihood%20activity%20for%20visually%20challenged%20individuals%20because%20they%20possess%20sharp%20sensory%20abilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20methods%20are%20simple%20yet%20effective%2C%20allowing%20both%20less-educated%20and%20well-educated%20individuals%20to%20learn%20acupressure%20massage%20systematically%20and%20scientifically.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20our%20course%2C%20students%20learn%20anatomy%2C%20physiology%2C%20and%20various%20massage%20techniques%20practically.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20they%20become%20experts%20in%20the%20field%20of%20acupressure%20massage%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20individuals%20are%20trained%2C%20they%20can%20return%20to%20their%20native%20village%20and%20practise%20there%20or%20stay%20at%20the%20centre%20and%20earn%20at%20least%20Rs%20500%20per%20massage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20also%20helps%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20get%20married%20and%20start%20a%20home.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20society%20looks%20at%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20especially%20women%2C%20in%20villages%20and%20small%20towns%2C%20is%20concerning.%20If%20an%20individual%20wants%20to%20get%20married%20to%20someone%2C%20we%20take%20their%20responsibility%20and%20help%20them%20with%20all%20the%20arrangements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20have%20facilitated%20over%2050%20marriages%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-12-1712585541.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harishchandra%20Sude's%20son%20Prashant%20who%20now%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20operations.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-12-1712585541.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-12-1712585541-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-12-1712585541-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-12-1712585541-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fleather-12-1712585541-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346855%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarishchandra%20Sude%E2%80%99s%20son%20Prashant%20now%20heads%20of%20the%20operations.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVidnyan%20Masure%2C%20a%20visually%20impaired%20person%20from%20Nanded%2C%20experienced%20prejudice%20all%20her%20life.%20She%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20very%20depressed%20and%20had%20low%20self-esteem.%20I%20even%20tried%20to%20end%20my%20life.%20However%2C%20joining%20GSP%20changed%20my%20life%20completely.%20I%20registered%20to%20learn%20massage%20therapy%20and%20I%20am%20now%20fully%20independent.%20I%20work%20in%20a%20naturopathy%20centre%20in%20my%20village%20and%20also%20teach%20this%20art%20to%20young%20visually%20impaired%20girls.%E2%80%9D%20The%2037-year-old%20is%20now%20happily%20married%20and%20feels%20a%20sense%20of%20dignity%20and%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20NGO%20came%20up%20with%20another%2