y%20and%20live%20a%20life%20full%20of%20love%2C%20happiness%20and%20dreams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20unconventional%20upbringing%2C%20her%20parents%20allowed%20her%20and%20her%20sister%20to%20dream%20big%2C%20work%20during%20junior%20college%2C%20have%20different%20life%20experiences%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20go%20abroad%20for%20an%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20unheard%20of%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardika%20worked%20summers%20after%20finishing%20Class%2010%2C%20where%20her%20first%20job%20was%20working%20as%20a%20market%20researcher%20for%20shampoo%20fragrances.%20After%20that%2C%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20font%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20before%20going%20to%20college%2C%20I%20had%20to%20create%20fonts%20for%20Indian%20languages%20on%20the%20computer.%20Since%20they%20wanted%20someone%20who%20could%20handle%20computers%20and%20had%20an%20artistic%20mind%2C%20I%20got%20the%20job%20and%20worked%20there%20for%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346774%2Fbengaluru-residents-saving-water-scarcity-rainwater-harvesting-recycle-greywayer-aerators-restrictors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBengaluru%20resident.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hardika%20started%20Kinara%20Capital%20in%202011%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170-500x262.jpg%20500w%2